Graphic: Graphic (tool for drawing graph-theoretic graphs)
Graphic:
Graphic: Graphic facilitates the drawing of graphs, particularly those
Graphic: with high degrees of symmetry.  It can output drawn graphs
Graphic: in a large variety of image formats as well as TikZ code for
Graphic: inclusion in TeX, LaTeX, or ConTeXt documents.
Graphic: It allows the user to save created drawings in a "graph library"
Graphic: for later reuse or modification.
